      "id": "architecture", "type": "text", "x": -700, "y": 20, "width": 700, "height": 380, "color": "4",
      "text": "## мӢӨн–ү м•„нӮӨн…ҚмІҳ (n8n-style WorkflowEngine)\n\n```\nOrchestratorService.startCritique(creationId)\n  вҶ’ DomainRegistry.get(slug)  // domains/{slug}/domain.json\n  вҶ’ domain.workflow.config     // workflow.json\n  вҶ’ WorkflowEngine.execute(workflow, context)\n      вҶ’ [agent-select]  м—җмқҙм „нҠё 5лӘ… м„ нғқ (domain strategy)\n      вҶ’ [round-execute]  parallel-first вҶ’ sequential\n         вҶ’ [llm-call]  critique-prompt-builder + provider\n         вҶ’ [persist-response]  DB м ҖмһҘ\n         вҶ’ [sse-broadcast]  мӢӨмӢңк°„ м „мҶЎ\n      вҶ’ [convergence-detect]  round-limit (max 3)\n      вҶ’ [synthesis]  вҳ… лҸ„л©”мқёлі„ format лқјмҡ°нҢ…\n```\n\n### мӣҢнҒ¬н”ҢлЎңмҡ° м„Өм • (domain/workflow.json)\n```json\n{ \"extends\": \"standard-critique\",\n  \"config\": {\n    \"maxRounds\": 3,\n    \"convergenceStrategy\": \"round-limit\",\n    \"synthesisFormat\": \"critique-novel\",\n    \"roundMode\": \"parallel-first\"\n  } }\n```"
    },
